    • setOpenTags

      public void setOpenTags​(java.lang.String openTags)
      Description copied from interface: IRequest
      Sets the list of EMV tags for Fast track operation, that must be returned to ECR in raw TLV view without encryption.
      Specified by:
      setOpenTags in interface IRequest
      Parameters:
      openTags - The string formatted by next pattern: Every tag must be coded by 4 byte on text hex view. For the example, tag DF82 looks like as 0000DF82 and tag 82 looks like 00000082. Multiple tags writes as 0000DF8200000082. This string may be begun from 0x prefix. Case type may be any.
